18/12/2009
PODGORICA, Montenegro -- The government announced a swine flu epidemic in the country Thursday (December 17th).
Health Minister Miodrag Radunovic said that health and school authorities are carefully monitoring the spread of the H1N1 virus.
He added that there are 244 confirmed cases so far.
(RTCG, Radion Antena M - 17/12/09)
